.Sh DESCRIPTION
The fifth argument to the
.Fn sqlite3_carray_bind
interface musts be one of the following constants, to specify the datatype
of the array that is being bound into the carray table-valued function.
.Sh IMPLEMENTATION NOTES
These declarations were extracted from the
interface documentation at line 11323.
